Description: DuckBotOS hybrid mode — Hermes + OpenClaw with session picker
 Installs both Hermes and OpenClaw agents along with the DuckBotOS
 session picker web UI. At boot, users see a choice between:
 .
   [1] Hermes    — Fullscreen kiosk with Hermes Web Dashboard
   [2] OpenClaw  — Fullscreen kiosk with OpenClaw workspace
   [3] Hybrid    — GNOME desktop with both agents in a side panel
 .
 This is the most feature-complete DuckBotOS experience. Both agents
 are always running; you pick which interface to use per-session.
 .
 Dual-agent IPC: Hermes and OpenClaw coordinate via the agent bus
 (/run/hermes-claw/agent-bus.sock) and share the Newest Desktop Control
 (Lobster Edition) MCP server for desktop control, plus trycua/cua for
 programmatic VM orchestration.
